</strong></li>
 	<li><strong>Available at: </strong>The early data is published in research papers by Broadberry and others. An overview is given in Broadberry (2013)[ref]This is taken from Broadberry (2013) ‚Äì <a href="http://voxeu.org/article/accounting-great-divergence">Accounting for the great divergence</a>.[/ref] The data for several European countries for the time period 1870‚Äì2000 is available online at Broadberry's website <a href="http://www.lse.ac.uk/economicHistory/whosWho/profiles/sbroadberry.aspx">here</a>.<strong>
